                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "sVlf2",
                  "fill": "#A0A0A0",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "From intimate corporate retreats to large-scale sports tournaments, we bring the same level of passion, precision, and creativity to every project. Our approach combines strategic planning with genuine care for each participant's experience.",
