              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 800,
              "content": "The Premier Cricket League Season 4 is the most anticipated inter-corporate cricket tournament in Bangalore. Organized by TriCore Events, this season brings together teams from top tech companies competing across multiple sporting disciplines over six action-packed days.",
