            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "OrFXH",
              "name": "rulesBody",
              "fill": "#A0A0A0",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 800,
              "content": "1. All participants must carry valid company ID for verification.\n2. Teams must have minimum required players present at match time.\n3. Match timings are strictly followed. Late teams forfeit the match.\n4. Umpire decisions are final and binding.\n5. Any form of misconduct will result in immediate disqualification.\n6. Registration fees are non-refundable after the deadline.\n7. Participants must wear appropriate sports attire.\n8. TriCore Events reserves the right to modify the schedule.",
